|the timestamp of the event
|-
|Sint32
|'''which'''
|the joystick device index for the SDL_CONTROLLERDEVICEADDED event or instance id for the SDL_CONTROLLERDEVICEREMOVED or SDL_CONTROLLERDEVICEREMAPPED event
